name: sumi:(inked) *special* VAPORWAVE PIG
description: You can easily spot the vaporwave Pig in a herd because its tats will turn white. As soon as it happens, QUICK, take a photo of it and look at it. The shot will automatically look as if it went through a vaporwave filter and the Pig's tats will glimmer. No matter the device you used. Example is shown here.
